Title: Sacred Temple the Cosmic energy ‚ö°Ô∏è

A temple of forgotten wisdom located deep among the magical Alps. a well-kept library rich of trade secrets for gathering and effectively using heavenly energies

The quest of the explorer who found the buried temple is shown in this picture. He was shocked to see two unearthly beings guarding it. He is attempting to navigate the temple complex with confidence despite the many uncertainties that are paralysing his head.

It's unclear what will happen next. You are welcome to use your imagination and to discover more.
